---
title: Bengali Roast Pumpkin & Currant Biryani  with Yoghurt & Flaked Almonds
description: This pilaf is packed full of flavours and colours, with green beans, currants, and roasted pumpkin all contributing to the rainbow!
Like a hug in a bowl, this warming dish is the perfect comforting meal.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
